        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Reduce visual noise with grayscale, friends-only filters, and optional custom script injection.
        </p>
        <span class="inline-block bg-foreground/10 text-foreground rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm">Reclaim focus</span>
